# Soccer AI Coach — environment template. Copy to `.env` and fill in real values.
# Client-safe values only. Get these from Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API.
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=your_publishable_or_anon_key

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SERVER-ONLY secrets — these NEVER go in the app (no EXPO_PUBLIC_ prefix) and
# are NOT read from this file. Set them as Supabase Edge Function secrets so the
# analyze-video function (Step 3) can call Claude server-side. See
# supabase/functions/README.md for the exact commands.
#
#   supabase secrets set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
#
# - ANTHROPIC_API_KEY         → your Anthropic API key. Server only; would leak
#                               billing if shipped in the client.
# - SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY → auto-injected into every Edge Function by the
#                               platform; you do NOT set it yourself. Bypasses Row
#                               Level Security, so it must never reach the app bundle.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
